videos.headline: Cal turnover problems continue with fumble
videos.description: Cal's Patrick Laird runs for 6 yards and fumbles with UCLA's Adarius Pickett recovering the football.

videos.headline: UCLA's Kelley punches in a  5-yard TD
videos.description: UCLA's Joshua Kelley takes the handoff and runs in for a 5-yard touchdown putting UCLA on the board.

videos.headline: UCLA's Kelley runs in a 1-yard TD
videos.description: Joshua Kelley punches in a 1-yard touchdown to extend UCLA's lead to 20-7.

videos.headline: UCLA's Kelley digs in 3rd rushing TD
videos.description: Joshua Kelley drives in a 1-yard touchdown, his third of the night.

videos.headline: UCLA's Lucier-South hauls in first career INT
videos.description: On 4th-and-1, UCLA's Keisean Lucier-South tips and grabs his first career interception.

videos.headline: UCLA's Keisean Lucier-South scoops and scores
videos.description: Cal's Brandon McIlwain is stripped and sacked with UCLA's Keisean Lucier-South recovering it for a 38-yard touchdown.
